# ---- Unreal Engine generated / build output ----
Binaries/
DerivedDataCache/
Intermediate/
Build/

# Saved/ is generated, including SaveGames. The fresh-save seed regenerates a
# fully configured save (100 points, ults slotted), so a committed .sav would
# shadow that seed on fresh clones.
Saved/*

